7 One (1) Wine chillers;
7 Three (3) Glycol chillers (In conjunction with Refrigeration Plant #1);
7 One (1) Ice maker(In conjunction with Refrigeration Plant #1);
7 Several relief valves, gas regulating valves, gate valves, solenoid valves, check valves, level switches, expansion valves; and
7 Piping and other ancillary equipment. The system contains about 16,000 lb. of anhydrous ammonia that continuously circulates through the system.  Vaporization of ammonia at different points of the system provides the needed cooling effect.  

